[REVISION 20070214]

[NEW] option to have stylesheets named for layouts added just after the RAILS_ENV stylesheet. Layouts are looked for in stylesheets/layouts/layout_name.css.

[REVISION 20061202]

[CHANGED] Use Rails 1.2 alias_method_chain.

[CHANGED] Separate modules into individual files.

[REVISION 20060726]

[NEW] First attempt at supporting paths for modules. Ie. an action of A::B::C#action would check for: a.css; a/b.css; a/b/c.css; and finally a/b/c/action.css.

[REVISION 20060717]

[CHANGED] Placed code into module named after the class to which the mixin will be applied.
